title: Toyota Camry 2.5 Hybrid Luxury
description:
Private Vehicle
Brand warranty valid until 2029, with a complete service history.

This vehicle is in excellent condition, Luxury version, nearly fully equipped with all possible extras for this model.
Protected with transparent PPF film on areas most prone to scratches, and all windows are tinted except for the windshield.

Main Features:
- Keyless Entry - keyless opening/closing
- Electric Steering Wheel
- Electric Rear Seats with control console (curtains, temperature, sound, etc.)
- Head-Up Display - projects information onto the windshield
- JBL Sound System with Subwoofer and 9 speakers
- Comprehensive Active Safety Systems: Lane Keep Assist, Adaptive Cruise Control, Emergency Braking, Collision/Blind Spot 360° Warning, Hold system, and more
- Automatic Headlights and High Beams
- Heated Seats
- Suspension and Steering with Three Settings (Eco, Normal, Sport)
- Wireless Smartphone Charging
